{"questionId":"17355","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Consider&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f\\left( x \\right) = \\frac{{2x - 4}}{{{x^2} - 1}}{\\text{, }} - 1 < x < 1\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>For the graph of&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y = f\\left( x \\right)\">\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>,</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>find the coordinates of the <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y\"> <mi>y</mi> </math></span>-intercept.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>(0, 4)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"17355","referenceCode":"19N.1.AHL.TZ0.H_10b.i","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"find the coordinates of the y -intercept.","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","AHL 2.13—Rational functions"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}